Login
---------------------
* Open the Getir application
* Wait for "7" seconds
* Click on the Get Started button
* Wait for "4" seconds
* Click on the Continue as Guest button
* Wait for "4" seconds
* Click on the New Getir Icon
* Wait for "4" seconds
* Click on coordinates X: "100", Y: "200"
* Wait for "2" seconds
* Click on profile icon
* Wait for "2" seconds
* Change language and go back
* Wait for "3" seconds
* Is the Canli Destek text visible?
* Add Address
